{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Play up to wave 20 of the first game mode!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">7 of 49 Turrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">10 of 96 Perks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fewer mods &amp; mutations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">All 70 weapons!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/extras/Banner_A.png?t=1728580140\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/extras/Banner_One.gif?t=1728580140\" /><strong>Dive into a microscopic alien world, radiating with bioluminescent life and unspeakable horrors.</strong> The free demo will give you a taste of what's in store in the full game - try out all 70 of the base game's weapons, get to grips with the weapon-combining mechanics, and research permanent upgrades  <strong>(you'll keep your progress &amp; unlocks in the full game!)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/extras/Banner_G.png?t=1728580140\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/extras/Banner_Synthesis.gif?t=1728580140\" /><strong>Pair DNA nucleotides Adenine (rapidfire), Cytosine (precision), Guanine (spread), Thymine (explosive) to discover wild hybrid bioweapons!</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Bomb + Shotgun</strong> combines explosives with spread to create <strong>Blast Shotgun!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Bomb + Bomb</strong> doubles down on explosive power to make <strong>Bazooka!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Blast Shotgun + Shotgun</strong> forms the all-powerful <strong>Flak Cannon!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Learn more about each weapon and microbe from the in-game database containing all your discoveries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/extras/Banner_C.png?t=1728580140\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/extras/Banner_Reroll.gif?t=1728580140\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Mutations</strong> alter the challenges you face each run</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>All 75 Bassy Electronic Tunes</strong> from the Full Game  adapt to the current mood &amp; intensity</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Accessibility Options</strong> for colourblindness and motion sickness</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cloud Save</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Plays great on Steam Deck!!!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/extras/Banner_Discord.png?t=1728580140\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728580140","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/page.bg.jpg?t=1728580140","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/851e4cd3ce1d7ad978eabf71077375053d99716d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728580140","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269290/851e4cd3ce1d7ad978eabf71077375053d99716d/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728580140","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","i